snippet.title: Super Sec Soccer trailer
snippet.description:
Super Sec Soccer is a simple local multiplayer soccer game for 2 players with all those bothersome rules stripped away so all you're left with is fast and easy fun!

http://www.supersecsoccer.com for more info.

Also on Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=341986765
